    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S. This 996.2 powerhouse features the 3.6L flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus timing, delivering linear torque through a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The wide-body chassis utilizes Turbo-spec suspension geometry and an all-wheel-drive system with a flawless viscous coupling. Mechanically superior, this example has a documented IMS bearing retrofit and zero evidence of bore scoring. The braking system features four-piston monoblock calipers over ventilated, cross-drilled rotors, providing surgical stopping power. Every bushing is compliant, the seals are airtight, and the engine exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders. A turn-key masterpiece for the purist driver.",
